No. 506,

Misc.

Brubaker v. Dickson, Warden. Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted. Quentin Ogren for petitioner. Stanley Mosk, Attorney General of California, and Arlo E. Smith and John S. Mclnerny, Deputy Attorneys General, for respondent.

Supreme Court of California. Certiorari denied.
